{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303620/extras/Banner_Steam.gif?t=1731488690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heartweaver is a 3D puzzle adventure game about loss and healing.\u00a0Follow the journey of Ace and Mark through Ace's twisted mind and help her reconnect with her feelings. Explore beautiful dark worlds that bring Ace's psyche to life, use her emotions to solve puzzles, recover her memories and help her weave a path towards\u00a0healing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u3164</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303620/extras/connect_with_Ace_s_emotions.png?t=1731488690\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help Ace free her repressed emotions. Connect through her feelings with her mental blocks and dissolve them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303620/extras/Connect_rasgado.gif?t=1731488690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u3164</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303620/extras/solve_puzzles.png?t=1731488690\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rearrange Ace's confused mind. Solve puzzles to clear her thoughts and see things clearly.\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303620/extras/Buyublin_rasgado.gif?t=1731488690\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u3164</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303620/extras/use_emotional_abilities.png?t=1731488690\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move forward by using the abilities of Ace's s